<header class="header--masthead">
  <div>
    <h1 class="white-ydtd-logo centered large">Your Day Their Day</h1>
    <h2>Spending too much time fighting for <em class="highlight-primary">resource?</em></h2>
    <p>
      Introducing YDTD—an online service designed for Creative agencies.
      It helps them to be more organised and makes resource planning a breeze.
    </p>
